com.davidbracewell.collection

Interface Index<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type parameter
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMapListIndex, ForwardingIndex

    public interface Index<E>
extends Iterable<E>

    An index represents a mapping from an Item to an id.

    Author:
    David B. Bracewell
